        <Parent_String>Romanesque Revival [300021467], modern European revival styles [300021442], modern European styles and movements [300021424], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
